Description
Table of Contents
Ask a Question




        OI S.A. - Strategy and SWOT Report, is a source of comprehensive company data and information. The report covers the company’s structure, operation, SWOT analysis, product and service offerings and corporate actions, providing a 360˚ view of the company.
Features:
- Detailed information on OI S.A. required for business and competitor intelligence needs
- A study of the major internal and external factors affecting OI S.A. in the form of a SWOT analysis
- An in-depth view of the business model of OI S.A. including a breakdown and examination of key business segments
- Intelligence on OI S.A.’s mergers and acquisitions (M&A), strategic partnerships and alliances, capital raising, private equity transactions, and financial and legal advisors
- News about OI S.A., such as business expansion, restructuring, and contract wins
- Large number of easy-to-grasp charts and graphs that present important data and key trends
Highlights:
Oi S.A. (Oi or “the company”) is an integrated telecommunications provider offering services to residential and business customers. The company primarily operates in Brazil. Oi is headquartered in Rio de Janeiro, Brazil and employed 36,739 people as of December 31, 2012.  The company recorded revenues of BRL25,169.2 million ($12,919.4 million) during the fiscal year ended December 2012 (FY2012) compared to revenues of BRL9,245.3 million ($4,745.6 million) in FY2011. The revenues primarily increased due to the consolidation of the results of Telemar and its subsidiaries as part of the company's corporate reorganization. The operating profit of the company was BRL4,760.1 million ($2,443.4 million) during FY2012 compared to an operating profit of BRL1,567.3 million ($804.5 million) in FY2011. The net profit was BRL1,784.9 million ($916.2 million) in FY2012 compared to a net profit of BRL1,005.7 million ($516.2 million) in FY2011.
Reasons to Purchase:
- Gain understanding of  OI S.A. and the factors that influence its strategies 
- Track strategic initiatives of the company and latest corporate news and actions 
- Assess OI S.A. as a prospective partner, vendor or supplier
- Support sales activities by understanding your customers' businesses better
- Stay up to date on OI S.A.’s business structure, strategy and prospects        
