 Oi S.A.: Notice to the Market - Moody’s rating 
         










    










 






 











 









Oi S.A.: Notice to the Market - Moody's rating

Oct 07, 2015, 09:31 ET
		  		  					
						 from   Oi S.A. 











 
















































 

 




















 


RIO DE JANEIRO, Oct. 7, 2015 /PRNewswire/ -- Oi S.A. (BOVESPA: OIBR3, OIBR4; NYSE:   OIBR.C, OIBR) (the "Company" or "Oi") discloses to its shareholders and the market in general that Moody's announced yesterday its revision of the credit rating attributed to the Company, downgrading the long-term global scale credit rating to Ba3 from Ba1 and certain obligations of the Company to B1 from Ba2. The outlook is negative.
Flavio Nicolay GuimarãesChief Financial Officer and Investor Relations Officer
Oi S.A.Corporate Taxpayers' Registry (CNPJ/MF) No. 76.535.764/0001-43Board of Trade (NIRE) No. 33.300.29520-8Publicly-Held Company
 SOURCE  Oi S.A.  




  

